vote.title: Authorize acquisition of a drainage easement containing approximately 3,644 square feet of land from A.J. Wallace and wife, Marilyn Wallace, located at East Woodin Boulevard near its intersection with Fernwood Avenue for the Kings Branch Culvert at Woodin Project - Not to exceed $13,700.00 ($10,700.00, plus closing costs and title expenses not to exceed $3,000.00) - Financing: 2024B Certificate of Obligation Fund
